Meet <b>Big_T_Dog</b>, our citizen of the week!<br><br>Big_T_Dog lives at <a href='/home/?user=big_t_dog'>2393 Windy Court</a>, where he has a great view of the lake.  He moved into the neighborhood of Lakeview on October 28th of 2004, and during his time here he's made it perfectly clear that he really loves living in Millsberry!<br><br>Big_T_Dog's friends enjoy hanging out with him because of his friendly personality.  If there is ever a dispute between two people, Big_T_Dog will gladly step in to help, usually managing to smooth things over with his charming personality.  After a few minutes of talking to him, the two sides will hardly remember what they were so angry about!  Due to his very compassionate nature, he's always more than happy to help others work out their problems.<br><br>Big_T_Dog is well-known amongst his classmates at Millsberry Academy for his outstanding athletic ability.  Though his favorite sport is football, Big_T_Dog plays a number of different sports well, as his trophies for Rope Race, Sink the Three, and Home Run Derby indicate.<br><br>When he's not out on the playing field, Big_T_Dog can usually be found indoors, listening to music and playing on his computer.  In fact, he's been known to occasionally tinker with combining these two interests by actually making music on his computer!  At other times, though, he is content just listening to a CD of modern rock or heavy metal.<br><br>After school, you can often find Big_T_Dog hanging out with his friends at the Millsberry Arcade, his distinctive backwards yellow baseball cap easily recognizable as it hovers over different games.  When he's not at the Millsberry Arcade, you can sometimes find him working to keep his other favorite hangout place clean - Peabody Park.  And, as if that weren't enough, from time to time he'll even take a break from his busy schedule to help out the Millsberry Police in their search for Millsberry's most wanted crooks!<br><br>Thanks for being a fine citizen, Big_T_Dog, and congratulations on being named Millsberry's citizen of the week!</div>
